Meta-layer containing only the Neutrino recipes (neutrino-mp, libstb-hal,
plugins, themes) for Tuxbox-OS on OE-Alliance platforms.

Notes
-----
- Yocto release: Kirkstone (4.0 LTS)
- Only Neutrino-specific bits live here: core Neutrino recipes, plugins/themes,
  libstb-hal, Neutrino packagegroup (`packagegroup-tuxbox-neutrino`).
- All generic distro, middleware, connectivity, toolchain, firmware, Qt/Kodi
  and miscellaneous support recipes remain in `meta-tuxbox`.
- Classes, licenses and waf cross-answers are provided by `meta-tuxbox`.

Usage
-----
Add both layers to `bblayers.conf`:

    BBLAYERS += "/path/to/meta-neutrino /path/to/meta-tuxbox"

